						               													<description>In 2107, two planets are on the verge of an interstellar war. As the vanguard commander of AstroSnipe, your mission is to navigate through black holes and chaotic asteroids between the planets and snipe at the enemy's planet to make the first strike!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Qloxx: AstroSnipe is a 2-player abstract strategy game about connections and obstructions in the size of a matchbox! By laying down and replacing the 9 Pathway tiles on the board, you control your troops' laser to shoot down enemy fleets and establish safe encampments for back-ups. The side that first strikes the enemy Home Planet will claim victory!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players place place or remove tiles on the centre board, or exchange one for another from hand.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends and you win when the enemy Planet Tile (like the King in chess) is removed from the board. The game may also ends in a draw if both players are exchanging the same 3 tiles on the same spot for over a full cycle.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
